---
---
<section id="formacion" class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-bg-primary relative select-none">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 md:px-12">
    <!-- Header de sección -->
    <div class="reveal text-center mb-16">
      <span class="font-mono text-xs text-accent-secondary uppercase tracking-widest block mb-3">Formación</span>
      <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-text-primary mb-4">Educación & Certificaciones</h2>
      <p class="text-text-secondary max-w-xl mx-auto text-xs sm:text-sm">Mi preparación académica y mis acreditaciones oficiales internacionales.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Bento Grid Académico -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 w-full mb-20">
      
      <!-- Hito 1: ITP -->
      <div class="reveal bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm hover-glow flex flex-col justify-between gap-6 relative group overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-28 h-28 bg-accent-secondary/5 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-accent-secondary/10 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-bold text-accent-secondary uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">2013 - 2018</span>
          <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-extrabold text-text-primary group-hover:text-accent-secondary transition-colors duration-300">Ingeniería en Tecnologías de la Información y Comunicación</h3>
          <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-secondary mt-1">Instituto Tecnológico de Puebla</h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed border-t border-border-custom pt-4">
          Formación completa en arquitectura de software, bases de datos y telecomunicaciones, estableciendo una sólida base técnica en desarrollo de sistemas empresariales.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Hito 2: Liderazgo Santander -->
      <div class="reveal bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-3xl p-6 sm:p-8 shadow-sm hover-glow flex flex-col justify-between gap-6 relative group overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute -right-10 -bottom-10 w-28 h-28 bg-[#bf5af2]/5 rounded-full blur-2xl pointer-events-none group-hover:bg-[#bf5af2]/10 transition-all duration-500"></div>
        <div>
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] font-bold text-[#bf5af2] uppercase tracking-wider block mb-2">2020</span>
          <h3 class="text-base sm:text-lg font-extrabold text-text-primary group-hover:text-[#bf5af2] transition-colors duration-300">Diplomado en Comunicación, Trabajo en Equipo y Liderazgo</h3>
          <h4 class="text-xs font-semibold text-text-secondary mt-1">Universidad Santander</h4>
        </div>
        <p class="text-xs sm:text-sm text-text-secondary leading-relaxed border-t border-border-custom pt-4">
          Especialización integral en habilidades directivas aplicadas a equipos multidisciplinarios de alto rendimiento, comunicación asertiva y negociación estratégica.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Certificaciones Grid -->
    <div class="reveal mt-16 w-full">
      <h3 class="text-lg sm:text-xl font-extrabold text-text-primary text-center mb-10">Acreditaciones Internacionales</h3>
      
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        
        <!-- Cert 1: PMP -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">💼</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">Project Management Professional (PMP®)</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">PMI • ID: 3192323</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cert 2: CSM -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">🛡️</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">Certified Scrum Master (CSM®)</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Scrum Alliance</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cert 3: PMI-ACP -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">🔄</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">Agile Certified Practitioner (PMI-ACP®)</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">PMI</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cert 4: ITIL -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">⚙️</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">ITIL® Foundation Certification</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">AXELOS</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cert 5: Google PM -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">📊</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">Google Project Management</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">Google / Coursera</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cert 6: Scrum Foundation -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">🧩</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">Scrum Foundation Professional</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">CertiProf</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cert 7: Lean Six Sigma -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">🎯</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">White Belt Lean Six Sigma</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">IKSS Association</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Cert 8: Cyber Security -->
        <div class="bg-bg-card border border-border-custom rounded-2xl p-5 flex flex-col gap-3 hover-glow shadow-sm">
          <div class="w-9 h-9 bg-bg-secondary border border-border-custom rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center text-base shrink-0">🔒</div>
          <div>
            <h4 class="text-xs font-bold text-text-primary">Cyber Security Foundation</h4>
            <span class="block text-[8px] text-text-muted mt-1 uppercase tracking-wider font-semibold">CertiProf</span>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
